PrecisEnactment of REGULATIONS DESIGNATING CERTAIN COUNTRIES FOR THE PURPOSES OF TARIFF ITEM NO. 9810.00.00, 1999-1 which designate 56 countries for the purposes of that Tariff Item number, thereby allowing them to bring in military supplies and other goods needed for military exercises and training while in Canada, on a duty-free and tax-free basis.
